  "content": {
    "intro": "The Bull Attorneys partnered with KAKE for its annual toy drive Sunday morning and there was no shortage of cars as they lined 21st Street.",
    "sections": [
      {
        "heading": "",
        "content": "The Bull Attorneys partnered with <span class=\"text-green-600\">KAKE</span> for its annual toy drive Sunday morning and there was no shortage of cars as they lined 21st Street. It was a one-stop shop as cars drove up exchanging toys for a mini stuffed bull donning the Bull Attorney logo. From there, cars moved on to get the shredding done that for some, looked as though they saved documents from all of 2023. Bull Attorneys will take the toys to the <span class=\"text-green-600\">Ronald McDonald House</span> where less fortunate kids will have a memorable Christmas."
      },
